	div.preview
		div.container.preview__container
			picture.preview__img
				source(srcset="images/map.png", media="(min-width: 1170px)")
				img(src="images/map-mobile.png", alt="Map")
			div.preview__slogan
				span.preview__slogan-text Работающий проект
				span.preview__slogan-text Real team
				span.preview__slogan-text Exciting perspectives
			div.pre-sale.preview__pre-sale
				div.pre-sale__inner
					span.pre-sale__name Till pre-sale start
					div.timer.pre-sale__time
				button.button.button--green.pre-sale__button(type="button")
					span Grab tokens at
					span.button__underline-text 0.1 ETH
	div.container
		section.section.about#about
			div.about__container
				div.about__inner
					h1.title.title-m.about__title ICOVoting
					div.about__description
						p.
							ICOVoting - a unique information and rating platform on ICO startups for crypto investors, experts, analysts, journalists and people
							involved into crypto activities from all over the world. The project team developed, implemented and successfully operates a unique system of open
							rating ICO projects through expert voting on the blockchain technology.
						p.
							ICOVoting was founded in December 2017.
				div.about__in-numbers
					span.about__text At the moment ICOVoting is:
					div.about__amounts
						div.about__amount
							span.about__number 6 800
							span.about__amount-name registered users
						div.about__amount
							span.about__number 10 000
							span.about__amount-name unique users per month
						div.about__amount
							span.about__number 1 500
							span.about__amount-name registered ICO
			div.about__wrapper
				span.about__main The trust of users and crypto-investors from around the world!
				a.button.button--big.button--green.about__link(href="https://icovoting.com", target="_blank")
					span visit
					span.button__underline-text icovoting.com
			div.ico.about__ico
				div.ico__container
					h2.title.section__title.ico__title Why do we launch an ICO?
					div.ico__description
						p.
							We want to make our project better and more useful for everyone.
							We are going to expand the existing services and add some more, so that more people can use ICOVoting in their work.
							We also want to launch an active promotion on the Internet and mass media.
				div.ico__container
					h2.title.section__title.ico__title What does our token give?
					div.ico__description
						p.
							Our token gives an opportunity to purchase advertising on our website and on the partners' websites.
							Our token - an advertisment on our website and it can be exchanged for cryptocurrency at the prices of the advertising market.
							Our token allows you to invest in expensive advertising of tomorrow at very attractive prices of today.
							We develop the project with your help, increasing website traffic that leads to higher prices for advertising on ICOVoting.
		section.section.plans#plans
			h2.title.section__title.plans__title Our plans:
			div.plans__inner
				ul.list.plans__list
					for elem in plans1
						li.plans__list-item
							svg.plans__icon
								use(xlink:href="images/sprite.svg#icon-circle")
							div.plans__text
								p #{elem}
				ul.list.plans__list
					for elem in plans2
						li.plans__list-item
							svg.plans__icon
								use(xlink:href="images/sprite.svg#icon-circle")
							div.plans__text
								p #{elem}
		section.section.token#token
			h2.title.section__title.token__title How to spend tokens:
			div.token__container
				div.token__sales
					div.token__sale
						span.token__sale-text Buy advertising on
							a.link.token__sale-link(href="https://icovoting.com", target="_blank") ICOVoting.com
					div.token__sale
						span.token__sale-text Exchange for cryptocurrency in our exchanger
						span.token__sale-date (this summer)
					div.token__sale
						span.token__sale-text Sell on the stock exchange
						span.token__sale-date (this summer)
				div.token__buy
					div.timer.token__buy-time
					button.button.button--green.button--small.token__buy-button(type="button")
						span Grab token at
						span.button__underline-text 0.1 ETH
		section.section.token-sale#token-sale
			h2.title.section__title.token-sale__title Token sale stages
			div.token-sale__container
				div.token-sale__inner
					div.token-sale__stage
						span.token-sale__stage-name 1 stage
						span.token-sale-date - 16.04.18 - 01.05.18
						span.token-sale-text Price 0.1 ETH - 1 000 VTS
